UID:20260501-1443374@ukmovies
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260501
SUMMARY:森中有林
DESCRIPTION:Runtime: 0 minutes\nRating: 0.0\nGenres: Drama\, Romance\, Crime\n\nThe story chronicles four decades in the lives of a family deeply rooted in the soil of Northeast China. Through times of prosperity and hardship\, they navigate cycles of love and hatred\, fortune and misfortune. Though buffeted by the twists of fate\, they never relinquish their steadfast guardianship of one another and the profound commitment to this ancestral land that sustains them.\n\nTrailer: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SczqyZQRpAo
END:VEVENT

